An Ansible Playbook using Package module:
--------------------------------------------

*** Package - a module used to install/ remove packages.

# Below Playbook install and remove the httpd from the system

--- 
- name: install a package
  package:
     name: httpd
     state: present

- name: install the latest version of a package
  package:
     name: httpd
     state: latest

- name: remove a package
  package:
     name: httpd
     state: absent

# Below Playbook task install the 'tmux' software on to the node

- name: Install the tmux package
  package:
     name: tmux
     state: present
